  "title": "Guest Relations Associate",
  "description": "<p><strong>Details:</strong></p><ul><li>Shift Hours: Morning (7am-4pm), Afternoon (1.30pm-10.30pm), Mid (10am-7pm), Night (10.15pm-7.15am)</li><li>5 Days a week (including weekends)</li><li>Central area</li></ul><p></p><p><strong>Duties:</strong></p><ul><li>Welcomed guests and handled check-in and check-out procedures efficiently</li><li>Built strong guest engagement by anticipating needs and maintaining attentive service throughout their stay</li><li>Delivered high-quality customer service by addressing guest requests and concerns and coordinating with internal teams for timely resolution</li><li>Managed reservations, email inquiries, room inventory, and room assignments during shifts</li><li>Coordinated with Revenue and internal stakeholders to support pre-arrival arrangements for VIPs, corporate clients, and group bookings</li><li>Monitored and optimised room inventory to support new sales opportunities and reservations</li><li>Promoted extended stays and upsold services to achieve individual and team sales targets</li><li>Identified opportunities for service improvement and personal development</li><li>Maintained accurate guest records in PMS and relevant systems</li><li>Ensured full compliance with SOPs, service standards, and operational guidelines</li></ul><p><br /><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Minimum of 1 year of experience in a similar role in the hospitality or customer relations industry</li></ul><p><br />Interested Applicants, please click Apply Now</p><p><br />Chow Zi Qing<br />R2199258<br />Revup Proservices Pte Ltd<br />EA.24C2366</p>",
